rows.label: campfev11_740_100_msg0001
rows.name: So. The time has come at last.

rows.label: campfev11_740_100_msg0002
rows.name: Indeed.

rows.label: campfev11_740_100_msg0003
rows.name:
Hugo. I'm sorry I dragged you
this far into all of this.

rows.label: campfev11_740_100_msg0004
rows.name: Not at all.

rows.label: campfev11_740_100_msg0005
rows.name:
The Holy Grail needed to be stopped.
I wasn't about to shy away from
the task.

rows.label: campfev11_740_100_msg0006
rows.name:
Stopping Metsu is just as much a
service to Superbia as it is to Iira.

rows.label: campfev11_740_100_msg0007
rows.name:
Laura I feel I must apologize to you
as well.

rows.label: campfev11_740_100_msg0008
rows.name:
Did you ever imagine, when we ran
into each other in Felt, that we'd
end up here?

rows.label: campfev11_740_100_msg0009
rows.name:
No, I can't say that I did...
But don't worry about it.

rows.label: campfev11_740_100_msg0010
rows.name:
I feel like defeating him is my
destiny too.

rows.label: campfev11_740_100_msg0011
rows.name:
I've met so many people in such a short
time...got to know them, seen them
laugh and cry...

rows.label: campfev11_740_100_msg0012
rows.name:
And I've gained friends I'm
never going to forget.

rows.label: campfev11_740_100_msg0013
rows.name:
There are lots of things in this world
worth protecting. So that's what I'm
going to do.

rows.label: campfev11_740_100_msg0014
rows.name: Well said...

rows.label: campfev11_740_100_msg0015
rows.name:
That was so moving, I think
I'm going to...*sniff*...

rows.label: campfev11_740_100_msg0016
rows.name: Adel, not again!

rows.label: campfev11_740_100_msg0017
rows.name: I'm serious...

rows.label: campfev11_740_100_msg0018
rows.name: We're going to win. How can we not?

rows.label: campfev11_740_100_msg0019
rows.name: Absolutely.

rows.label: campfev11_740_100_msg0020
rows.name: Of course!
